  Once you have added resources and exercises to the Topics section of the Learning Plan, you  
 can create assignments that deliver those materials to your students. 

  <p><b>Create an assignment plan</b></p>

  <p>Add an introduction, indicate assignment rules, set the start and end date, etc.</p>

  <p><b>Add topic(s) to the assignment</b></p>

